The weapon fire echoed of Megatron's knee, as it forced him to do a
front flip, and then, lose control of his flight. He fell to the ground,
landing on his back in a sickening thud, his fusion cannon becoming
disloged, and falling behind him. His knee smoked for a bit, and then
stoped, but he didn't move.
